251
00:09:53,974 --> 00:09:56,395
What the heck does yoga have to do with animation?

252
00:09:57,232 --> 00:10:01,335
Well, one reason I love yoga so much is because the things you learn in a class are really

253
00:10:01,335 --> 00:10:03,676
applicable to all areas of your life.

254
00:10:03,676 --> 00:10:07,839
One thing you hear all the time in yoga class that I really love is, go to the uncomfortable.

255
00:10:07,839 --> 00:10:12,383
I know it's a little cheesy and we've heard it a lot, but we often gravitate towards the

256
00:10:12,383 --> 00:10:14,104
things that we're already good at.

257
00:10:14,104 --> 00:10:17,426
But we're not going to grow as much if we only do those things that we're comfortable

258
00:10:17,426 --> 00:10:17,867
